BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:2026 Chicago St Patrick's Day Bar Crawl Saturday All Access CT
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260314T120000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260314T180000
UID:260313MZ1Nq-kN30e4xQRuIAQYpw
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/axWQn4vIfk2iwj7Wrou_Sg.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Special Perks from HolidayBarCrawls.com HERE: https://www.even
 tbrite.com/e/2026-chicago-st-patricks-day-bar-crawl-saturday-all-access-ti
 ckets-1363938319229?aff=chicagotribune&discount=3rd30\n\n“Luck Of The Ir
 ish Is With You This St Patrick’s Day”\n\n\\*Max Attendance For This E
 vent Is 499 People\, Almost Sold Out - Once Sold Out - We Have No More Tic
 kets\\*\\*\n\nLimited Tickets On This Big Holiday - Buy Before Its Too Lat
 e\n\nCalling all Irish jig leprechauns\, four-leaf clover wearers\, Irish 
 lovers\, those with green clothes and who love green beers ...\n\nTake you
 r tribe of hooligans on a St Patrick’s Day adventure at the 2026 St Patr
 ick’s Day Bar Crawl taking place Saturday\, March 14\, 2026 at several l
 ocations presented by Social Scene. Enjoy over 30 venues in 3 neighborhood
 s! From Irish jigs\, DJs\, live bands & the must-have green drink cheers
 … the St Patrick’s Day Bar Crawl is the perfect place to celebrate thi
 s green-filled Irish holiday with those you care for the most.\n\nOur Temp
