 ortalimages/portalimages/BeeSA5H830aUTaADdMNMCw.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Chicago Chorale presents The Peaceable Kingdom\, a renowned ch
 oral work by American composer Randall Thompson that was inspired by the p
 rimitivist painting of the same name by Edward Hicks.  The concert will a
 lso feature motets by Briggs\, Centeno\, Clausen\, Howells\, Palestrina\, 
 Pärt\, and Paulus.
