DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260314T120000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260314T150000
UID:251209lasFxfdBb0-vV7RczAvDjQ
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/vyd5o3g-WU-C5A9ZJtoGng.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The North Shore Camp Fair is a free\, in-person summer camp
  expo happening on Saturday\, March 14 in the Louis Room inside the No
 rris University Center at Northwestern University in Evanston\, IL. More 
 than 50 day camps\, overnight camps\, specialty programs\, and more will
  be onsite to share information about their offerings. Admission is comple
 tely FREE\, giving you the chance to explore a wide variety of outstandin
 g summer opportunities all in one convenient location.\n\nIf you’re a fa
 mily in the Evanston area searching for the ideal summer program for your 
 child\, this event is a must-attend. It’s truly the quickest and easiest
  way to compare camps. Rather than contacting each camp individually\, you
  can meet and talk with representatives from all of them at once at the N
 orth Shore Camp Fair!
LOCATION:Northwestern University
URL:https://www.coasttocoastcampfairs.com/north-shore-camp-fair.html
X-SOURCE:Evanston Roundtable
