 wiss Rounds with a cut to the top players\n\nCapacity: 32\n\nPrizes are aw
 arded to the top players in each of the three age divisions. To earn point
 s and prizes\, players must have a\n\nPokémon Trainer Club\n\naccount wit
 h a Player ID attached and must have opted into the\n\nPlay! Pokémon\n\np
 rogram. All participants will receive 1\n\nPlay! Point\n\njust for playing
 .\n\nPrizes:\n\nEach player will receive $4 store credit for participation
