UID:2603131b3yN3TflE6ZjP7ZieHeLw
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/9vaeQn8-x0uXBJl8GkLplA.large.png
DESCRIPTION:What happens when two best buddies with over a decade of music
 al improv experience are given complete creative control!? A whimsical\, t
 oe-tapping\, extraordinary delight of the senses that will have you belly 
 laughing\, singing along\, and getting our songs wedged DEEP in your brain
 ! Come watch as improvised beatbox extraordinaire Brian “B-Sticky” Mes
 lar and viral comedian/master guitarist Ross Childs take up their position
 s as wacky commentators for different special events each performance nigh
 t. Like most special events\, the evening will be full of wildly enjoyable
  scenes and moments\, infectiously hilarious commentator banter\, and- of 
 course- bombastic song and dance numbers \\(all based on your suggestions\
 \). So please! Join us for the premiere of what will surely be one of the 
 most riotous\, rambunctious\, revolutionary musical improv experiences eve
 r created!!!!!! Next month’s show TBA!
LOCATION:Otherworld Theatre
URL:https://www.choosechicago.com/event/a-witty-ditty-committee/
X-SOURCE:Evanston Roundtable
END:VEVENT
