ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/ADuGa2zALU-IBku9FDbfcQ.large.png
DESCRIPTION:One of the Girls is a one-of-a-kind Irish band and must-see en
 tertainment every March around St. Patricks Day. Our music celebrates the 
 spirit of the Irish diaspora in America with high-energy arrangements\, th
 ree-part harmonies\, and an unmatched sense of fun\, humor\, and genuine n
 ostalgia. Uptempo bluegrass-inspired interpretations of your favorite trad
 itional Irish music\, heartfelt Ballads that honor and respect the old hom
 eland\, and maybe even an unexpected cover tune or two will keep you tappi
 ng your foot and singing along. So grab a pint\, join us for some tunes\, 
 and wonder how in heavens name these gentlemen are One of the Girls!
