BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Surrounded crowd work show
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T190000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T000000
UID:260224rfG_Mz0NNUCCw4UUlJ-ikQ
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/osXyxzQdrUi1QEc4CN9kpg.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:"Surrounded" is a popular\, critically acclaimed stand-up come
 dy show designed entirely around crowd work\, where comedians perform in t
 he center of the room\, surrounded by the audience. \n\nKey details about 
 the show include:\n\nFormat: The show utilizes a "theater-in-the-round" se
 tting. There is no traditional stage\; the comedian stands in the middle\,
  and the audience sits entirely around them.\n\nPremise: The show is "all 
 crowd work\," meaning comedians perform without prepared material\, relyin
 g on improvised interactions with audience members to create the show's co
 ntent.\n\nCreator: The show was created and is hosted by comedian Mike Fal
 zone.\n\nLocations: It originated at the Hollywood Improv Lab in Los Angel
 es and regularly plays at The Stand NYC.\n\nFeatures: It has been featured
  at major comedy festivals\, including JFL in Montreal\, Moontower\, and N
 etflix is a Joke Festival.\n\nVirtual Reality: The show has also been adap
 ted for a VR experience on Meta Horizon Worlds. \n\nSurrounded is known fo
 r being an unpredictable and highly interactive experience\, where the aud
 ience becomes part of the show.
LOCATION:kibbitznest books\, brews & blarney
URL:https://www.bandsintown.com/e/107927048?app_id=pkvts0on0m&came_from=28
 7&utm_medium=api&utm_source=partner_api&utm_campaign=event
X-SOURCE:Evanston Roundtable
END:VEVENT
