BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Sydny August & Cailin Russo
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T200000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T000000
UID:2602243FEWceDpZ0C9pA7PvJyaBA
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/J1wRUrvkbUmZYN_2EbfU9A.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Cailin Russo is a multi-hyphenate artist whose creative output
  is currently focused on music. Her forthcoming album Influx \\(2022\\) ha
 s been her sole pursuit of the last two years\, with intermissions taken t
 o work with Kanye West and walk in fashion shows. Known for her avant-gard
 e lyricism and production\, innate sonic taste and evocative style\, Caili
 n’s subtle yet hypnotic presence is as potent online as IRL\, with a loy
 al fan base since her modelling days and a digital network of over 2 milli
 on. \n\nGrowing up in San Diego\, Cailin’s early musical inspirations st
 emmed from an eclectic mix of genres including pop punk\, rap\, and jazz\,
  with lifelong touchstones coming in the form of iconic female musicians A
 my Winehouse and Gwen Stefani. Russo cites James Blake\, FKA twigs and Kan
 ye West as her current favourites\, with the latter personally asking Cail
 in to assist in the production of his last album Donda. Cailin went on to 
 be nominated for a Grammy by the Recording Academy for her work on West’
 s track ‘Hurricane’.\n\nOn the opening track of her new album INFLUX\,
  Cailin Russo muses ‘In the back of my mind there’s a white hearse or 
 a limousine.’ The breathy\, distorted statement is repeated\, reverberat
 ing before shattering into a sexy R&B dreamscape sliced by the line ‘all
  I feel is everything’. Cailin Russo is an artist who embodies and expre
 sses the conflicts and complexities of the multiple truths that coexist wi
 thin our modern identity - the everything - living in the fantasia of her 
 own manifestation\, the white hearse and the limousine. \n\nAside from her
  musical career\, Cailin is a staple face and presence in the LA creative 
 scene\, with modelling gigs for it-girl brands I AM GIA and Skims\, Helmut
  Lang and Rodrarte\, handpicked for the front row of shows at New York and
  Paris fashion weeks\, and seen as both a cultural mainstay and innovator 
 who stands the test of both time and trend. Having graced the covers of Ga
 lore\, Wonderland and Roller Coaster and received rave reviews from Billbo
 ard\, Rolling Stone\, and MTV\, Cailin is stepping into an era of sharply 
 contemporary sound\, carving out her own space in the pop world.\n\nhttps:
 //twitter.com/cailinrusso\n\nhttps://instagram.com/cailinrusso\n\nhttp://c
 ailinrusso.com
LOCATION:Subterranean
URL:https://www.bandsintown.com/e/1038044956?app_id=pkvts0on0m&came_from=2
 87&utm_medium=api&utm_source=partner_api&utm_campaign=event
X-SOURCE:Evanston Roundtable
END:VEVENT
