ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/FZ3dU49TTE-Y4dw1Yke1WQ.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Experience an unforgettable night of wonder at Magic Mondays!!
  Starring award-winning magician John Sturk\, this monthly showcase featur
 es Chicago’s top conjurors performing mind-blowing illusions and spellbi
 nding tricks. Join us for an evening of magic\, mystery\, and mesmerizing 
 entertainment—perfect for magic lovers and those looking for a night out
  with a twist! Don’t miss your chance to witness the impossible. \n\n  
 \n\nJohn Sturk is an award-winning comedy magician from Chicago. He has be
 en seen on ABC\, NBC\, WGN\, Fox\, and The Travel Channel. He’s also gra
 ced the stages of The Second City\, iO Chicago\, The Annoyance Theater\, M
 alarkey Comedy\, and countless living rooms and backyards throughout the m
 idwest. In 2023\, he served as National President of The Society of Americ
 an Magicians\, the oldest magic association in the world. \n\n  \n\nIn ad
 dition to magic\, John is also one of Chicago’s most accomplished music 
 directors\, having been seen behind the keyboards of Chicago’s comedy in
 stitutions. He also is an official artist for Hammond Organs USA.  \n\n 
  \n\nMagic Mondays is recommended for ages 12 and up.
