DESCRIPTION:Audrey Stewart is a Los Angeles-based actress and stand-up com
 edian. She is a regular at the Hollywood Improv and is currently in Develo
 pment at the World Famous Comedy Store. She also performs at clubs around 
 the world. In 2023\, she was named a New Face at the Just for Laughs Festi
 val in Montreal\, Canada\, and performed at the 2024 Netflix Is a Joke Fes
 tival in Los Angeles. Additionally\, she sold out her headlining show at t
 he New York Comedy Festival this past year. Stewart has appeared on NBC\, 
 The Drew Barrymore Show\, Netflix Is a Joke Radio\, National Lampoon\, Ame
 rica's Funniest Home Videos\, and Facebook Watch\, and has a set with Don
 ’t Tell Comedy. She is also a cast member of the new YouTube prank serie
 s from the creator of Punk'd\, called Prank U.
LOCATION:Zanies Comedy Club
