SUMMARY:Justin Parlette
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260318T193000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260318T000000
UID:260227XsX8_Zloz0SiURfT5-hADQ
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/YL7xnn2JBkqvwZvnvBzInQ.large.png
DESCRIPTION:The legacy of The Free Show\, dating back to the early days of
  Improv Olympic\, has helped make long-form improv accessible to audiences
  of all backgrounds. That tradition continues with Dumb John and Birdlady.
 \n\nRegarded as one of Chicago’s funniest and most promising improv grou
 ps of the last decade\, Dumb John joins Birdlady for a new weekly long-for
 m double feature. Both teams bring a high-energy strain of improvisation t
 o a bizarre cultural harvest of small-town Americana influence and ephemer
 a\, using a single audience suggestion to launch an unhinged long-form rid
 e: diesel-soaked characters\, fever-dream karaoke scenes\, neon aisles of 
 roadside antique marts\, and whatever depravity and brilliance show up in 
 the moment.\n\nTake flight with two back-to-back original iO ensembles\, B
 irdlady and Dumb John\, every Wednesday night.\n\nThis is a FREE show\, bu
 t reserving a ticket is highly recommended to guarantee entry.\n\nDOORS: 7
 :00pm\n\nSHOW: 7:30pm\n\nBirdlady is:\n\nAli Khan\, Alonso Ramirez\, Chris
  Franz\, Daryn Robinson\, Devin Henderson\, Erin Washington\, Justin Parle
 tte\, Lauren Frost\, Ryan Nolan\n\nDumb John is:\n\nMike Geraghty\, Steve 
 Plock\, Linda Orr\, Traycie Mcbee
LOCATION:iO Theater
URL:https://www.bandsintown.com/e/107968313?app_id=pkvts0on0m&came_from=28
 7&utm_medium=api&utm_source=partner_api&utm_campaign=event
X-SOURCE:Evanston Roundtable
END:VEVENT
