ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/hPPlS8AVf0K4mcNI8gUGiA.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Free the Witness is a punk rock band from Asbury Park\, NJ. Es
 tablished in 2019. The band has slowly developed a niche sound that brings
  an electric blend of all your favorite 90s Epitaph and Fat Wreck bands mi
 xed with the operatic vocals of frontman Jake Bédel. They have most notab
 ly played alongside punk rock legends NOFX and Descendents as well as supp
 orting local heavy hitters School Drugs. Their most recent record “Dead 
 Man’s Tale”\, produced by Pete Steinkopf of The Bouncing Souls\, saw e
 ditorial support from the likes of both Spotify’s “All New Punk” & A
 pple’s “New in Rock” playlists. Free The Witness’ latest & viral s
 ingle “Drain Me” has proven that the band is not afraid to pivot into 
 new territories and explore new sounds as they head into 2026 preparing fo
 r new songs and consistent touring throughout the U.S.
LOCATION:Burlington Bar
URL:https://www.bandsintown.com/e/107812662?app_id=pkvts0on0m&came_from=28
 7&utm_medium=api&utm_source=partner_api&utm_campaign=event
