  relaxed sip-and-paint experience — create your own birdhouse or paint a
  prairie landscape while enjoying a drink and good company. Whether you co
 me with friends or make new ones\, it’s a fun way to unwind and tap into
  your creativity. We’re also excited to welcome back Holly Greenberg and
  her Birds of the Anthropocene project. \n\nAs a special bonus\, the first
  50 guests will receive a one-of-a-kind\, branded Nature Night Out pint gl
 ass. We hope you’ll join us for an engaging evening of nature\, creativ
 ity\, and community. \n\n  \n\nEvery ticket comes with 1 complimentary al
 coholic OR non-alcoholic beverage. Additional beverages and snacks will be
  available for purchase. \n\nWhether you can join us the whole time or for
