BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Orchid Show: Feelin' Groovy
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T100000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T160000
UID:260227tf3dXpBGIU-IT11SNLn52w
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/cb1ee9cf-dc61-4c69-82eb-f2684b83aafd.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Let the sunshine in! Step into a flowery\, technicolor rewind 
 to the ’60s and ’70s during The Orchid Show: Feelin’ Groovy. Attende
 es will experience pure good vibes with floor-to-ceiling sunbeams made of 
 cascading orchids\, getting lost among a 10-foot lava lamp aglow with colo
 rful blooms\, and daydreaming about hitting the road in a flower-filled Vo
 lkswagen Beetle.  The Orchid Show: Feelin’ Groovy opens on Saturday\, Fe
 bruary 7 and runs through Sunday\, March 22\, 2026. Regular hours are from
  10 a.m. to 4 p.m.
