  to Moulin Rouge\, certain musicals have had a revolutionary approach to c
 inematic storytelling. Challenging audiences with fresh and unusual styles
  of music and dance\, these films dared to break the rules and reinvent th
 e musical. Film historian Steve Frenzel provides clips from 42nd Street\,
  Cabaret\, Anchors Aweigh\, Flashdance\, and much more!  So many are you
 r favorites from the past and some beautiful\, but not as familiar.
