DESCRIPTION:Join us for Stark Bierfest Stammtisch on Friday\, March 20 fro
 m 7:30-11:00 PM as we celebrate a cherished Bavarian tradition. After the 
 revelry of Fasching comes the season of Lent - and with it\, Starkbier. Fi
 rst brewed in the 17th century by Paulaner monks\, including the famous Sa
 lvator\, this strong\, nourishing beer was crafted to sustain them through
  fasting and has since become a seasonal favorite across Bavaria. Raise a 
