DESCRIPTION:@  Sleeping Village Saturday\, March 21 Metro Presents… Chal
 k $20 Adv. / $25 Day of / 21\\+ / Doors: 7PM / Show: 8PM Chalk is the proj
 ect of award-winning musicians and filmmaker duo Ross Cullen and Benedict 
 Goddard. An informed mix of Dublin's Guitar Band scene and the sweaty hard
 core dance floors of their native Belfast\, Chalk are IDLES meets Daniel A
 very\, Death Grips meets Bicep-techno-infused industrial punk. Since formi
 ng in 2022\, Chalk have had a rise like no other\, quickly establishing th
 emselves as an unmissable live act and unpredictable\, ferocious songwrite
 rs. Their debut UK/IRE tour sold out\, and led to further bookings across 
 Europe as word of their performance and guitar-melded techno spread via wo
 rd of mouth and support with national radio in the UK. These songs were co
 llated into the Conditions Trilogy\, a family of thirteen tracks that comb
 ine gritty Irish and German-influenced techno and dance music with gothic\
 , post-punk and jagged guitar riffs and vocal melodies. This unique blend 
 earned them the support and kudos of their peers in Fontaines D.C.\, IDLES
  and Sprints\, all of whom handpicked the band to support them throughout 
 their tours.
LOCATION:Sleeping Village
