BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Jewel-Osco's Big Deal Battle Benefiting YMCA of Metropolitan Chica
 go
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260324T180000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260324T220000
UID:260310662PtL30jky_WvCscaWIYA
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/qeRVCQ2HnkyveoFhUQc7xg.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:JEWEL-OSCO's BIG DEAL BATTLE: A WRESTLING-INSPIRED SPECTACLE B
 ENEFITING YMCA OF METROPOLITAN CHICAGO\n\nTuesday\, March 24 | 6–10 p.m.
  The Salt Shed | 1357 N. Elston Ave.\, Chicago\n\nJewel-Osco is bringing b
 ig energy to Chicago with Big Deal Battle\, a larger-than-life wrestling-
 inspired entertainment event benefiting the YMCA of Metropolitan Chicago
 . Taking place at The Salt Shed\, the high-energy evening will feature 
 five professionally produced wrestling matches from fan favorite pro-wrest
 lers including Killer Kross vs. Matt Taven\, Shayna Baszler\, Mayari\, T
 he Good Brothers\, The Brothers of Funstruction\, Big Vito\, Ben Bishop\, 
 La Estrella\, and REAL1 \\(formerly Enzo Amore\\).\n\nFans can expect li
 ve commentators\, meet-and-greets with wrestling personalities\, photo opp
 ortunities\, interactive fan activations\, festive food and drinks\, givea
 ways\, and appearances by JoJo\, Jewel-Osco’s iconic mascot.\n\nFans mu
 st enter to win free tickets at celebratewithjewelosco.com by March 1
 6. Each entry also triggers a $1 donation from the Jewel-Osco Foundation 
