DESCRIPTION:Share the care\, one hug at a time! Love-a-Lot Bear will be ma
 king appearances at CAMP Chicago and can’t wait to meet you.\n\nGet read
 y for smiles\, sparkles\, and heartwarming fun — a very special Care Bea
 r is visiting CAMP\, and your family is invited to meet them! Each ticket 
 includes:\n\nA Meet & Greet photo opportunity with one Care Bears characte
 r\n\nA giveaway\, while supplies last\n\nA few other important notes:\n\nY
