BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Chicago Jazz Orchestra Septet's Freddie Green Tribute
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260327T193000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260327T193000
UID:260227xmEKGfmgDUai2EOLRLuYcw
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/L_MwQbPX4Ui4kmIOMCoTOw.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The Chicago Jazz Orchestra Septet celebrates Freddie Green’s
  115th birthday — who was Count Basie’s legendary guitarist for decade
 s — with Green’s recently discovered original charts. This exciting ev
 ening will feature Eric Schneider on saxophone\, Art Davis on trumpet\, Mi
 chael Petterson on guitar\, Reggie Thomas on piano and guest vocalist Alys
 sa Allgood. This concert will be recorded live for Chicago Jazz Live on W
