 ortalimages/portalimages/xqJnu92uQk6O8c5yW3Xcng.large.png
DESCRIPTION:The HIRS Collective exist to fight for\, defend\, and celebrat
 e the survival of trans\, queer\, poc\, black\, women and any and all othe
 r folks who have to constantly face violence\, marginalization\, and oppre
 ssion. We are a collective of freaks\, faggots\, friends\, lovers\, and fa
 vorites that will never stop existing. infinite and never ending. No one i
 s going to kill us\, we are going to live forever.
LOCATION:Subterranean
