 ortalimages/portalimages/kLj4iFEbC0aJy-HPt14O_w.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Adam Nate Levine is the midwestern rabbi telling street jokes 
 you never knew you needed. Originally from Ohio\, he started his comedy ca
 reer in Chicago before moving to New York City where he performs nightly a
 t New York Comedy Club\, Greenwich Village Comedy Club\, The Laugh Tour an
 d hosts a show\, A Fistful of Jokes\, in Brooklyn. His jokes have been on 
 The Onion\, House of Highlight's Clash Series and his pilot script\, Shul'
 s Out\, was featured at the Austin Film Festival. A commercial actor as we
 ll\, Adam can be seen for 2.3 seconds in a Harry's Razor ad. Adam's comedy
  festival credits include The New York Comedy Festival\, Windy City Comedy
  Festival\, Whale City Comedy Festival and he's opened for comedy heavywei
 ghts such as Jessica Kirson\, Brad Williams and Isabel Hagen.
LOCATION:Zanies Comedy Club
