BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Poetry Reading with The Honorable Angelina Nordstrom
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260331T190000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260331T203000
UID:260314lMZdN2CxxkWEf_VDP50dGQ
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/31Ug2cCI4Eui7PpXNizPtQ.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Zora’s Place for a powerful evening of poetry and
  reflection with local poet The Honorable Angelina Nordstrom.\n\nRooted in
  lived experience and spiritual reflection\, Angelina’s work explores wh
 at it means to move through the world holding multiple identities while re
 claiming power\, voice\, and wholeness.\n\nThis gathering is an invitation
  to listen\, witness\, and celebrate the beauty of authenticity\, resilien
 ce\, and transformation. Angelina will read from their poetry collection\,
  *DOUBLE SPIRIT: The Inner Union of the Sacred Feminine & the Divine Masc
 uline Identities*.\n\n**Event Details**\n\n• Doors open at 6:45 PM\n\n
 • Poetry reading begins at 7:00 PM\n\n• Audience Q&A to follow\n\n• 
 Books will be available for purchase at the event
LOCATION:Zora's Place
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/poetry-reading-with-the-honorable-angelin
 a-nordstrom-tickets-1984681972205?aff=oddtdtcreator#location
X-SOURCE:Evanston Roundtable
END:VEVENT
