 r through movement\, community\, and fun. From beginner-friendly clinics l
 ike Her First Dink! to social open play\, moms meet-ups\, and the signatur
 e Smash the Ceiling Invitational tournament\, this lineup welcomes players
  of all skill levels. \n\nEvents will take place at both SPF Lincoln Park 
 and SPF All Day in Irving Park\, Chicago’s premier indoor pickleball and
  social venues. Whether you’re brand new to the sport or a seasoned play
 er\, guests can enjoy expert instruction\, festive open play\, and a vibra
 nt\, supportive atmosphere celebrating women in sport. \n\nJoin SPF Pickle
 ball from March 2–8 for a week of connection\, empowerment\, and celebra
 tion on and off the court. Advance registration is recommended\, as space 
 is limited.
LOCATION:SPF Pickleball Chicago
URL:https://www.choosechicago.com/event/international-womens-day-week-at-s
 pf/2026-04-01/
X-SOURCE:Evanston Roundtable
END:VEVENT
