 ortalimages/portalimages/SDfr7M16WkWtYdDM2o92jA.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Mid America is the Western folk rock duo of Mia Carruthers and
  Curtis Roush. Their music lives in the mythology of the forgotten middle
 —songs shaped by endless highways\, unseen towns\, and the quiet resilie
 nce of those who endure there. Rooted in the craft of 70s record-making\, 
 they build upon tradition with harmonies and guitar work that feel both ti
 meless and fiercely alive. Their debut\, Moving Nowhere Incredibly Fast\, 
 embodies that restless spirit.
