BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Spring Egg-Stravaganza at Lincoln Park Zoo
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260404T074500
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260404T114500
UID:260206vUJbn0_QyE2cAYBuU7Qm5g
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/rrUZ5aFvDEKQtOx8Ojux7Q.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Ready\, set\, EGGS! Spring Egg-Stravaganza has returned to Lin
 coln Park Zoo\, and you’re invited to hop on over for a day of springtim
 e fun. Children ages 1–8 can gather colorful eggs\, snap photos with the
  Easter Bunny\, dance and clap along to musical entertainment\, meet frien
 dly zoo experts\, and more. \n\nFor egg hunt\, choose from six distinct zo
 nes of varying difficulty levels\, terrain\, and potential zoo animal spec
 tators. With timed-entry tickets\, participants can join the fun at their 
 own pace. Learn more about the egg hunt zones. \n\nAll Tickets Include: \
 n\nEntry starting at 7:45 a.m.—come before your little one’s egg hunt 
 time and enjoy the rest of the event!\n\nUnlimited rides on the Endangered
  Species Carousel\n\nUnlimited rides on Lionel Train Adventure\n\nFace pai
