DESCRIPTION:Following directly from Come On and Get It\, Judiths outstandi
 ng new album Yet to be named can only be described as the full Judith Owen
  experience\, celebrating all of her strengths and everything that has bro
 ught her joy throughout her last three releases. It combines the joyous sw
 agger of her wildly successful Come On and Get It\, the hi-octane sounds o
 f her 2024 love letter to big band\, Judith Owen Swings Christmas\, the li
 ve power of Comes Alive\, and her own emotionally intoxicating songwriting
  and arrangements. A beautiful blend of jazz\, blues and big band it may b
 e\, but above all it shows off her inimitable sound that seamlessly unites
  all the tracks. Whether solo at the piano\, accompanied by her jazz trio\
 , sextet or her contemporary big band\, Judiths rich mellifluous voice sed
 uces\, and her interpretations\, thrilling.
