 broad support from the United States. However\, with new tariffs\, this mi
 ght be the start of a significant downturn. As consumers\, you benefit fro
 m products made in other countries. Gene Flynn examines the positives and 
 negatives of international trade\, and discusses how it affects prices\, i
 nvestments\, corporate decisions\, and many other issues both here and abr
 oad.
