BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Logan Michael with  CARV
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260409T200000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260409T200000
UID:260127Ixwi0GlozE-7cwYJVhlAkA
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/pMGHTPsv8E6U_gim2ExaMw.large.png
DESCRIPTION:18\\+ with Parent or Guardian / www.carolspub.comYoung rising 
 country singer Logan Michael has taken humble beginnings and turned them i
 nto a burgeoning career as one of the most exciting new faces in the genre
 . His cool\, cutting baritone paired with heartfelt\, lovesick lyrics abou
 t the frenetic and often toxic uncertainty of young love has captured wide
 spread attention\, helping him connect with the next generation of country
  fans and beyond.Logan originally broke out on TikTok with his viral singl
 e Angel Wings. Since then\, he has used the platform to steadily grow his 
 fanbase\, gaining over 300\,000 followers by posting song clips and captio
 ns that resonate deeply with his audience. While hes enjoying the momentum
  of his breakout success\, Logan remains grounded in creating the kind of 
 music he grew up loving.Raised in North Attleboro\, Massachusetts\, Logan 
 spent his childhood listening to his dads old Alan Jackson CDs a foundatio
 n that would later inspire him to teach himself guitar in high school. I w
 ould say the reason I make country is partially my upbringing and what I l
 istened to growing up\, but also just the meaning and stories country song
 s bring to the table\, Logan says. You can tell a real story in each song\
 , and theres just something about it thats special to me. Its real.Realnes
 s is at the core of Logans music. His emotional track Leave Me Alone explo
 res the difficulty of letting love into your life when you feel unworthy o
 f it\, capturing the tension between vulnerability and self-protection in 
 moments of darkness.After releasing his EP Hope For Tomorrow in 2022 and f
 ollowing up with standout singles like Another Go\, Whiskey Serenade\, and
  the breakout hit Breaking Point\, Logan surpassed 1 million monthly liste
 ners on Spotify. He continued his rise in 2024 with the releases of Said a
 nd Done and Have a Nice Day\, and in 2025 signed with Rebel Music/Gamma\, 
 releasing new tracks including I Met This Girl and Make It. A new project 
 is currently underway.Logan has also shared the road with artists such as 
 Gavin Adcock\, Chayce Beckham\, Brantley Gilbert\, Tyler Hubbard\, and Kid
 d G\, and is preparing for a year of headline touring in 2025 something he
  has long looked forward to. His goal is to bring the authentic connection
  he fosters on social media into an intimate live setting.I could be singi
 ng to 20 people or 20\,000 as long as someone feels what Im saying\, thats
  good enough for me.With a soulful twang to his vocals and a tireless work
  ethic that keeps him consistently delivering for his listeners\, Michaels
  limitless potential is set to blossom into a fully-fledged new school ris
 ing star in Nashville.This event is 18\\+ with a parent or guardian. Any t
 icket holder unable to present valid identification indicating that they a
 re at least 18 years of age\, and have a parent or guardian present\, will
  not be admitted to this event\, and will not be eligible for a refund.GA 
 Tickets do not include seating. Reserved Table purchase includes entrance 
 to the show and a reserved table for the designated number of people.Pleas
 e arrive 30 minutes prior to showtime to claim your table. If your party h
 as not arrived by that time\, your table may be subject to be given away t
 o another group and we will do our best to facilitate your group upon your
  arrival\, however a table is no longer guaranteed.
LOCATION:Carol's Pub
URL:https://evanstonroundtable.com/events/#/details/logan-michael-with-car
 v/17581041/2026-04-09T20
X-SOURCE:Evanston Roundtable
END:VEVENT
