 R 2026 at 07:00PM CDT\n\nAges: All Ages\n\nDoors Open: 06:00PM\n\nOnSale: 
 Fri\, 21 Nov 2025 at 10:00AM CST\n\nAnnouncement: Mon\, 17 Nov 2025 at 12:
 00PM CST\n\nRuslan KD is a Christian author\, YouTuber\, podcaster\, and e
 ntrepreneur whose work inspires millions to steward their time\, talent\, 
 and treasure for God’s glory. An Armenian refugee from the former Soviet
  Union\, Ruslan’s journey—from immigrant beginnings to full-time creat
 ive ministry—embodies the themes of faith\, resilience\, and purposeful 
 living.\n\n \n\nHe is the author of Godly Ambition \\(WaterBrook/Penguin R
 andom House\, 2025\\)\, a book equipping believers to pursue calling witho
 ut losing their soul. On his YouTube channels\, Ruslan engages over a mill
 ion monthly viewers with thoughtful commentary on culture\, faith\, and pe
 rsonal growth\, interviewing leaders such as Patrick Bet-David\, Lecrae\, 
 and Eric Thomas.\n\n \n\nAs a sought-after speaker\, Ruslan has shared the
  stage at conferences\, universities\, and churches worldwide\, helping au
 diences navigate the tension between ambition and godliness with biblical 
 clarity and practical wisdom. His story continues to inspire a generation 
 to live intentionally\, build with integrity\, and make an eternal impact.
 \n\nFor ADA accommodations\, please email info@jamusa.com.\n\nNo backpacks
 \, bags\, laptops or tablets allowed in the venue. For a full list of proh
 ibited items\, please click here.
LOCATION:Park West
URL:https://www.facebook.com/events/1438061467930457/
