  social venues. Whether you’re brand new to the sport or a seasoned play
 er\, guests can enjoy expert instruction\, festive open play\, and a vibra
 nt\, supportive atmosphere celebrating women in sport. \n\nJoin SPF Pickle
 ball from March 2–8 for a week of connection\, empowerment\, and celebra
