BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Chicago World Oddities Expo
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260411T110000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260411T110000
UID:25102647-MJVDBbkWhklaPFT8nRg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/lqMvLBi3QUOZ6Rw1xn96iQ.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to WOE’s 3rd Annual Chicago Expo —prepare yourself
  for an experience like no other!\n\n \n\n ️ Saturday & Sunday\, April 1
 1th - 12th\n\n Donald E. Stephens Convention Center\n\n Halls C & D\n\n 
 ️ VIP 10am-7pm\n\n ️ General Admission 11am-7pm\n\nChildren 12 and und
 er are free!\n\n \n\n Welcome to the World Oddities Expo- a traveling cele
 bration of all things weird\, intriguing\, and magically macabre! We’re 
 combining our love of art\, history\, science and entertainment wrapped in
 to one incredible event! Shop till you drop from dozens of eclectic vendor
 s and small businesses. Grab a ticket to the Deformed Exhibit to indulge i
 n rare\, preserved specimens that defy the laws of nature! Take a workshop
  in WOE labs and try your hand at taxidermy\, rat skeleton articulation\, 
 or create a miniature diorama terrarium and more! Visit our Main Stage for
  amazing live performances throughout the day\, as well as surprise guest 
 speakers for free seminars! Whether you’re into oddities\, art\, fashion
 \, science\, or the culture- this is your space to celebrate what makes yo
 u unique! \n\n DEFORMED EXHIBIT\n\nVisit our touring\, one-of-a-kind Defor
 med Exhibit featuring real\, rare specimens with medical anomalies! Snag a
  combo general admission ticket or a combo VIP ticket for those who want e
 arly access to shop before the crowds.\n\n WOE LABS\n\nReady to kickstart 
 your new favorite hobby but aren’t quite sure how to start? Take a class
  at WOE Labs and enter a world where learning and creativity collide! Our 
 knowledgeable and experienced instructors are there to guide you step by s
 tep. Don’t stress- all experience levels are welcomed! Classes vary from
  city to city.\n\n✨️ LIVE ENTERTAINMENT \n\nWe curate only the best an
 d most talented performers to take the WOE stage! You’ll find everything
  from contortion\, odes to sideshow\, clowns\, as well as a few things you
 ’ve never seen before! Don't miss these jaw dropping performances at the
  WOE Main Stage throughout the day!\n\n✍️ ODDITY INK PARLOUR- Only in 
 select cities\\* Grab some new ink at the Oddity Ink Parlour and get a tat
 too on site! Sponsored by Villain Arts and only in select cities- we’re 
 bringing you talented artists from all over the country. Grab those VIP ti
 ckets so you can be first in line for an appointment! \n\nThis isn’t jus
 t an expo\; it’s an experience\, and you’re part of it. Get ready to j
 oin a community of people who celebrate the strange\, the wonderful\, and 
 the weird. We can’t wait to see you there—stay weird\, friend! \\#chic
 ago \\#oddities \\#festival \\#art\n\n ️ ➡️ Get your tickets NOW at 
 WORLDODDITIESEXPO.COM
LOCATION:Donald E. Stephens Convention Center
URL:https://www.facebook.com/events/1234856771792315/
X-SOURCE:Evanston Roundtable
END:VEVENT
