BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:GoldFord: Space of the Heart Tour
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260411T200000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260411T200000
UID:250924ytsS0AHdj0Cy_tGQB3YKPQ
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/BJltXemzFUmNEqJObxNJ8Q.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Jam Presents\n\nGOLDFORD: SPACE OF THE HEART TOUR\n\nSAT\, 11 
 APR 2026 at 08:00PM CDT\n\nAges: All Ages\n\nDoors Open: 07:00PM\n\nOnSale
 : Fri\, 26 Sep 2025 at 10:00AM CDT\n\nAnnouncement: Thu\, 18 Sep 2025 at 1
 0:00AM CDT\n\nGoldFord  is a singer-songwriter with a voice that carries w
 eight - rich\, emotive\, andunfiltered. With a timeless blend of pop and s
 oul\, he writes music rooted in truth\,\n\nvulnerability\, and healing. Hi
 s forthcoming EP\, “Space of the Heart”\, out September 26th\, promise
 s raw\, unfiltered songs that balance introspection with catharsis and\n\n
 grapple with heartbreak\, healing\, and the quiet revelations that come wi
 th growth\n\nand maturity.\n\nOriginally from St. Louis and now based in L
 os Angeles\, GoldFord’s journey to musicwas far from conventional. After
  a decade navigating corporate life\, a profound\n\npersonal loss sparked 
 a transformation. Music became not just a dream\, but a vitalexpression of
  purpose and resilience. His breakout single “Upside Down” announced  
 his arrival\, followed by the viral hit “Orange Blossoms\,” which garn
 ered over 70 million Spotify streams and earned co-signs from Sam Smith\, 
 SZA and Noah Kahan. \n\nAs he prepares to bring his new material to audien
 ces worldwide\, GoldFord will be\n\nembarking on his sold out UK and Europ
 ean tour in Autumn 2025. The tour includes\n\nhis highly anticipated UK he
 adline debut at London’s Scala on October 22 - a show\n\nthat has sold o
 ut and been upgraded due to overwhelming demand. With a growing\n\nfanbase
  and a distinctive sound\, GoldFord is set to make a lasting impact on the
 \n\nglobal stage
LOCATION:Park West
URL:https://www.facebook.com/events/2553105335030374/
X-SOURCE:Evanston Roundtable
END:VEVENT
