BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Antisemitism in Film: Ever Again (Hybrid)
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260415T130000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260415T160000
UID:260312_plcDo-G70CBn1qtz7Zacg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/w8kF8mxeGUCmFcopKwOWkg.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Jay Sorkin presents a 2025 documentary covering the aftermath 
 of the October 7\, 2023 attack and massacre by Hamas in Israel. The film 
 examines the 2023-2024 pro-Palestinian university campus protests after th
 e October 7 Hamas-led attack on Israel\, and exposes the organization and 
 preparatory work Hamas put in ahead of time to make them look spontaneous.
  You will discover the role of social media in allegedly stoking antisemit
 ism among young people\, and how it impacted this brutal event. (In Englis
 h\, 2025\, 1h 40 min)
LOCATION:North Shore Senior Center
URL:http://www.nssc.org
X-SOURCE:Evanston Roundtable
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Discover the National Park Service in Illinois and the North Shore
  Area
