 e\, guests can buy a Value Pack featuring 10 mini golf games for $89. The 
 in-venue-only offer runs throughout March and April\, making it easy to en
 joy multiple rounds of Puttshack’s tech-driven mini golf experience with
  friends and family.\n\nLocation: Puttshack Skokie 4999 Old Orchard Center
  Skokie\, IL 60077\n\nWebsite: https://www.puttshack.com/locations/skokie\
